body:
In the following example, when INOUT is ref, verilator displays "flag=0" in the second line, while VCS 2017.03 displays "flag=1".

```
//`define INOUT inout
`define INOUT ref

module automatic top;

  task update(`INOUT bit flag, input bit upflag);
    flag = upflag? 1: flag;
  endtask: update

  bit my_flag;
initial begin
  update(my_flag, 1);
  $display("flag=%d", my_flag);
  update(my_flag, 0);
  $display("flag=%d", my_flag);
  $finish();
end
endmodule;
```

Verilator version: Verilator 4.221 devel rev v4.220-24-gbaff64a4
